quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  95,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  95,1,qasam hai injeer aur Zaitoon ki
  95,2,aur tor seena ki
  95,3,aur iss pur aman shehar ( mecca ) ki
  95,4,hum ne ensaan ko behtareen saakht par peda kya
  95,5,phir ussay ulta phair kar hum ne sab نیچوں se neech kar diya
  95,6,siwaye unn logon ke jo imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay ke un ke liye kabhi khatam nah honay wala ajar hai
  95,7,pas ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) is ke baad kon jaza o saza ke maamla mein tum ko jhutla sakta hai ?
  95,8,kya Allah sab hakmon se bara haakim nahi hai ?
